# Keep every text file LF in the worktree as well as the repository.
# The CSP pins inline <script> blocks in index.html by SHA-256 of their raw
# bytes; a CRLF checkout on Windows silently changes those bytes, breaks the
# hashes, and CSP would then block the import map in production. eol=lf makes
# the working tree byte-identical to what GitHub Pages serves.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
